                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <b>ICAP</b> - With <small>ICAP</small> released, we're working on building forecasting and inspection tools for staking rewards.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <b>Multiple Addresses</b> - Ability to input multiple addresses at once, so that your portfolio view can correctly determine transfers between your wallets.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <b>Public API</b> - Whats the point in caching all this data if only I can use it?
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <b>Graphing and Exporting</b> - Further useful views and charts, coupled with the ability to export data into common formats like json, xml &amp; csv.
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </p>
                    </Answer>
                </Question>
